<h1 class="hero-h">Scaling a global fitness SaaS from <em style="color:#00C853;font-style:italic;">150 to 1,200+ operator locations.</em></h1>
<p class="hero-sub">A six-year fractional Head of Marketing & GTM Strategy engagement with Hapana, the global fitness operator platform. From an Australia-anchored studio software with 150 locations to a globally-deployed enterprise SaaS supporting more than 1,200 multi-location fitness operators across North America, EMEA, and APAC.</p>
<div class="headline-metric">
<div class="metric-num">800%</div>
<div class="metric-label">Revenue growth over the six-year engagement, supporting global expansion across three continents</div>
</div>
<div class="disclosure"><p>Named client engagement, published with the consent of the client. Specific revenue figures aggregated for confidentiality; growth multiples reflect actual results.</p></div>
</div></div>

